headline: eMoney Advisor Appoints Fred Pattin as Head of Finance
summary: eMoney Advisor (eMoney), a leading provider of technology solutions and services that help people talk about money, today announced the appointment of Fred Pattin to head of finance. Joining the firm's core leadership team, Pattin will report directly to CEO Susan McKenna.
